From: Claude <noreply@anthropic.com>
Date: Tue, 16 Jun 2026 11:48:11 +0000
Subject: [PATCH 5/8] Add OAuth integration flows for LinkedIn & HubSpot

- Create OAuth provider infrastructure (types, state management)
- Implement /api/oauth/authorize endpoint for provider redirect
- Implement /api/oauth/callback endpoint for token exchange
- Store OAuth tokens securely in workspace config (JSONB)
- Support token refresh and expiration tracking
- Add OAuthIntegrationCard UI component
- Show connection status and connected timestamp
- Handle OAuth errors gracefully with user feedback
- Support multiple OAuth providers (LinkedIn, HubSpot)
- Add OAuth success/error messages to integrations page

OAuth Flow:
1. User clicks "Verbind via Provider"
2. Redirect to provider authorization
3. Provider redirects back to /api/oauth/callback
4. Exchange code for token
5. Store in workspace.config.oauth
6. Return to integrations page with success message

Environment variables needed:
- LINKEDIN_CLIENT_ID / LINKEDIN_CLIENT_SECRET
- HUBSPOT_CLIENT_ID / HUBSPOT_CLIENT_SECRET
- NEXTAUTH_URL (for redirect URI)

